{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Ja22w3kUnaCiCTaGJwwtYq","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Verification Proof: Story 20-2 Summary Bar & Merge Status\n2\t\n3\t**Story:** 20-2-summary-bar-merge-status\n4\t**Tier:** test-provable\n5\t**Date:** 2026-04-04\n6\t**Verifier:** Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context)\n7\t\n8\t## Pre-flight Checks\n9\t\n10\tBuild: PASS (tsup ESM success, dist/index.js 423.98 KB)\n11\tTests: PASS (190 test files, 5103 tests, 0 failures)\n12\tLint: WARN (8 errors, 58 warnings — all pre-existing, none in story files)\n13\t\n14\t## AC 1: SummaryBar component exports and renders summary format\n15\t\n16\tFile `src/lib/ink-summary-bar.tsx` exists (2773 bytes). Exports `SummaryBar` function component and `SummaryBarProps`, `MergingEpicInfo`, `CompletedLaneInfo` interfaces.\n17\t\n18\t```bash\n19\tnpx vitest run --reporter=verbose 2>&1 | grep -E \"exports SummaryBar|renders done stories|exports correct types\" | head -5\n20\t```\n21\t```output\n22\t ✓ lib/__tests__/ink-summary-bar.test.tsx > SummaryBar component > exports SummaryBar as a function component 12ms\n23\t ✓ lib/__tests__/ink-summary-bar.test.tsx > SummaryBar component > renders done stories with checkmark symbols 35ms\n24\t ✓ lib/__tests__/ink-summary-bar.test.tsx > SummaryBar component > exports correct types 1ms\n25\t```\n26\t\n27\t## AC 2: SummaryBar renders \"Merging: —\" when no merge active\n28\t\n29\t```bash\n30\tnpx vitest run --reporter=verbose 2>&1 | grep \"Merging: —\"\n31\t```\n32\t```output\n33\t ✓ lib/__tests__/ink-summary-bar.test.tsx > SummaryBar component > renders \"Merging: —\" when no merge active 1ms\n34\t```\n35\t\n36\t## AC 3: SummaryBar renders merging epic with spinner when in-progress\n37\t\n38\t```bash\n39\tnpx vitest run --reporter=verbose 2>&1 | grep \"spinner when in-progress\"\n40\t```\n41\t```output\n42\t ✓ lib/__tests__/ink-summary-bar.test.tsx > SummaryBar component > renders merging epic with spinner when in-progress 2ms